Description:
An old warrior is resting near the remains of a draconoid patrol. When he notices your presence, he warns that the place is dangerous and advises you to leave before another patrol arrives.

Upon hearing that you are a group of adventurers on a mission, he sighs in relief. He reveals that he was the best murmillo the Velkarath Colosseum ever knew and was on a mission to defeat the frost dragon.

However, a wise warrior knows when to retreat, and age is taking its toll on him. If you prove that you know how to defend yourselves, he may give you a special arena badge to challenge Velkarath coliseum’s special trial.
DescriptionAction: Do you want the arena badge that he is offering?
